{"tid":186143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]九紋龍家中離世 (有片 有圖)","createTime":"2017-04-04T04:09:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-04T04:56:04.000Z","uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"df6ddcd8aaf0240b4ed08df1dba635828f64deae","tid":186143,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T04:09:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-G6PENtiVsw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-G6PENtiVsw&d=pyoTqnfnoeQhQMJnYGDXlJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=1cd6acb6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-G6PENtiVsw</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/04/120925_9260446f86a72cf416e66213ddd3097e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F04%2F120925_9260446f86a72cf416e66213ddd3097e.jpg&h=675abba9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/04/120926_e033ce38396064b5ed8195d3e84dce3e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F04%2F120926_e033ce38396064b5ed8195d3e84dce3e.jpg&h=d0ecfca9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曾參演過多部《陰陽路》系列電影的演員九紋龍（招浩強），今日在一個名為「香港車手會」的社交網專頁及討論區被貼出逝世的消息，終年52歲。<br />\n<br />\n據九紋龍身邊人表示，日前他曾向朋友透露感冒不適，其後身邊好友均無法和他聯絡。直到昨日（4月2日）警方到其寓所調查，經破門入內而發現他的屍體。九紋龍最後一部演出的作品為英皇電影《紮職》，戲中與譚耀文有一場爭執戲份。<br />\n<br />\n另外，他亦活躍賽車和足球活動，其社交網亦有上載與賽車手歐陽若曦和甄卓偉的合照。"},{"pid":"460d1e523db706b9759fb030401dc3a079418785","tid":186143,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T04:10:16.000Z","msg":"曾經打到 陳偉霆 重傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"113cd4863c471a08f84f5a3c3cf225d1bc4ab5d0","tid":186143,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T04:50:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8be4fb7f2c7a4cda7b9c1a87927c75c5dace7bff","tid":186143,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T04:56:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}